.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, time-travel, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, mexican, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, ship
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
2. the indian is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the mexican is the person watching epic movies##1
6. the argentine is the person driving the airplane##1
7. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
8. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | zombie     | epic   | time-travel      |
| Nationality   | indian    | argentine | mexican | nigerian  |
| Transport     | motorbike | airplane  | ship    | quad-bike |

