.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, r&b, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, weightlifting, soccer
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the person who's sport is surfing and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the person who's sport is soccer is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
7. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
9. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | d&b        | r&b        | rock   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | soccer   | surfing | basketball |
| Pet           | rabbit  | guinea-pig | fish       | ferret |

