1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cranberry is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
3. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in september##7
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
6. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
8. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food          | apricot   | cranberry  | tomato     | raspberry    |
| Birthday   | july   | january | september      | march |
| Sport         | badminton | rowing     | ice-hockey | skiing       |

