 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the scientist is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 3. the scientist is on the right of the journalist##1
 4. the fan of soul is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 5. the freelancer is somewhere between the fan of classical and the fan of electronic##7
 6. the freelancer is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 7. the scientist is the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of indie##1
10. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
